  "title": "Dietetic Assistant (Entry/Hospital) #HZO",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope: </strong></p><ul><li>Assist manager in administration work and nutrition-related matters</li><li>Assist in development of nutritional education material.</li><li>Write minutes and reports.</li><li>Update Dietetics Web page.</li><li>Participate in Quality Improvement Projects.</li><li>Assist dietitian in setting up nutrition education programs.</li><li>Assist dietitian in the development of slides for nutrition education.</li><li>Assist dietitian in internal / external departmental projects.</li><li>Assist dietitian in nutritional analysis using computer software.</li><li>Assist in appointment booking for patients.</li><li>Perform & document pre-clerking of patients, including social, medical, weight history, diet history, food frequency questionnaire, as needed.</li><li>Manage oral nutrition supplements (ONS) samples, ensuring no expired products, proper storage and\ntracking of samples.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Min. Diploma in any relevant food science/ nutrition field </li><li>Keen in dietitian industry </li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please send your updated resume to: melissa@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>All candidates’ information will be treated with the strictest confidence</p><p>Melissa Zhang Zhiqi (Mezzo)</p><p>R2197564</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>99C4599</p>",
